PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1991-1680, which fixed the rates of remuneration payable to the Co-Chairpersons and Commissioners of the Royal Commission on ABORIGINAL PEOPLES, adding actual and reasonable TRAVEL EXPENSES incurred by them while travelling outside Canada.
Attachments
precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1991-1680, which fixed the rates of
remuneration payable to the Co-Chairpersons and Commissioners of the
Royal Commission on ABORIGINAL PEOPLES, adding actual and reasonable TRAVEL
EXPENSES incurred by them while travelling outside Canada.
